CALL CLEAR_AI_DIPLOMACY_PLAN(相手勢力, 勢力)


持ち出し額 = MONEY:勢力 * AI_DIPLOMACY_PROPERTY:(COUNTRY_AI_TYPE:勢力):AI_外交_同盟支払額 / 100

